kforce, effective collaboration, ultimately performing better and achieving more accurate results.  Equitable leadership improves decision-making, and for-profit organizations can boost profitability, e.g. by expanding the customer base, identify new markets and decrease retention costs.<?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="d8126873-acab-4690-f225-f9c2cb4c7c96"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="8848353" change-id="5862f261-463a-4331-c58c-5c308d1c80e7" text=" . Teams within the organization are more creative, innovative, and collaborate more effectiveland . Organizations that support gender equality benefit from" timestamp="1670256077838"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-start author-id="5191008" change-id="93c68f5b-7c4a-470e-e5ee-311da4fd63b1" timestamp="1666090567904"?><?fontoxml-change-addition-end change-id="93c68f5b-7c4a-470e-e5ee-311da4fd63b1"?><?fontoxml-change-deletion author-id="9276395" change-id="a2d2eca9-d658-4e58-9676-01bab1006e02" text="]" timestamp="1675418545189"?></p><p/></sec>